description:
Since the first day of the first wave of the first lockdowns for ‘our health & safety’ I’ve seen fast food lines wrapped around the buildings out into the main streets holding up traffic. ⠀
⠀
Chick-Fil-A looks like a free crack house everyday.⠀
⠀
Popeyes holds up traffic every evening. ⠀
⠀
McDonald’s keeps a line 24/7.⠀
⠀
Krispy Kreme ran a graduation special an I saw myself a line that had to be 1-2 miles long. ⠀
⠀
Yet and still people are still buying the health pandemic agenda?? ⠀
⠀
Wearing a mask and gloves while getting your Big Mac, fried chicken, extra large coke, or freshly fried donuts from a drive-thru...with a mask on from a person with a mask on!?!?⠀
⠀
Only to follow every agenda backed lie and propaganda and now at the shore of of a wave of mandatory RNA altering vaccines for a cold and flu like illness with a 99.7% survival rate?⠀
⠀
Idk exactly what’s in store for humanity but I do know there’s a cosmic shift/reset in the energy and there are factions foaming at the mouth to implement their new ordering of the world (NWO) and if we sit back and allow we will not only be the guinea pigs but the ones in history responsible for ushering in and blindly accepting this wicked trajectory in humanity. ⠀
⠀
Stand for something. ⠀
⠀
